 8 datasets and 5 tasks, such as unsupervised\npart and saliency segmentation, recognition, and detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 17:59:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-07"}
