estimating the\nevaporation rate in tumble dryers are discussed. The review of the related\nliterature showed that all of the previous models for the prediction of the\nevaporation rate in the clothes dryers have some limitations in terms of\naccuracy and applicability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 08:11:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-10"}
