these three distinct behaviours, the decay rate of the\ndynamic structure factor is related to the static structure factor as if the\nsystem were completely linear. This quasi-linearity occurs regardless of the\nsize of $g$ and at all length scales. Numerical simulations confirm the\nexistence of the three classes of behaviour and the quasi-linearity of all\nclasses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 11:57:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
