tion. Notably, both\nsets of fully distributed schemes display near-optimal sample-complexities,\nsuggesting that this hierarchical structure does not lead to performance\ndegradation. Finally, we validate the proposed methods on a networked\nNash-Cournot equilibrium problem and a hierarchical generalization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 13:54:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-10"}
