\lceil \\frac{1}{2}n_1(G) \\rceil$. Finally, we show that if $G\\sim\nG(n,p)$ and $np\\ge 20$ then, with high probability, $\\hat{\\mu} (G)=\\mu (G)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 15:50:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-10"}
